fields.name: Poll 1
fields.yaml:
name: "Poll 1"
image: "https://external-content.duckduckgo.com/iu/?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.publicdomainpictures.net%2Fpictures%2F170000%2Fvelka%2Fsuperman.jpg&f=1&nofb=1&ipt=a2fc3be8cd1d24aedb1aac3181302ecc71e30ae0ebd215e79a76e7da799147d1&ipo=images"
allow: AUTH
res: '*'
poll:
    - info:
        type: LABEL
        text: "Example poll 1"
        label: "The purpose of this poll is to know what superpower people want and\n what they like to do on weekends."
    - superpower:
        required: true
        type: CHOICE
        text: "Which superpower would you rather have?"
        choices:
            - invis: "Invisibility"
            - tp: "Teleportation"
            - speed: "Super speed"
            - time: "Time manipulation"
    - weekend:
        required: true
        type: CHOICE
        text: "What's your favorite way to spend a weekend?"
        choices:
            - tv: "Binge-watching TV shows"
            - outdoors: "Exploring the great outdoors"
            - camp: "Camping"
            - game: "Gaming"

fields.name: Poll 2
fields.yaml:
name: "Poll 2"
image: "https://external-content.duckduckgo.com/iu/?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.publicdomainpictures.net%2Fpictures%2F280000%2Fvelka%2Fgolden-dragon-1543960150tr0.jpg&f=1&nofb=1&ipt=8d469af2d301eb2fff7f77bf68fe658c75df6347377e03cdbd2c4f30a6d7d5fa&ipo=images"
allow: AUTH
res: '*'
poll:
    - info:
        type: LABEL
        text: "Example poll 2"
        label: "The purpose of this poll is to know whather people prefer to go to the past or the future and\n what mode of transportation they like."
    - time:
        required: true
        type: CHOICE
        text: "If you could time travel, where would you go?"
        choices:
            - past: "Past"
            - cur: "I won't time travel."
            - fut: "Future"
    - transpt:
        required: true
        type: CHOICE
        text: "Pick a mode of transportation"
        choices:
            - dragon: "Flying on a dragon"
            - pirateship: "Sailing the seas on a pirate ship"
            - car: "Car"
            - bus: "The flying bus from Fortnite"
